{"tid":1240091,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"達致真普選/獨立既基本做法","createTime":"2019-06-18T09:15:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T09:25:25.000Z","uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6fcee70910de7cdfb14c851683079a99df3f426a","tid":1240091,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T09:15:55.000Z","msg":"1)長期抗爭,累積聲勢同人數<br />\n2)支持特朗普連任,到時記住幫手同五毛對打網戰<br />\n3)支持蔡英文連任,到時記住幫手同五毛對打網戰<br />\n4)加強宣傳真普選同獨立既好處<br />\n5)支持美國取消香港獨立關稅區地位,令中國失去逃生門同洗錢既地方<br />\n<br />\n以上呢D係最基本同成本最低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,無論真普選定獨立,都唔係單靠香港內部抗爭就可以達成,必須依賴多方面既打擊,所以要同其他反共勢力聯合/支持佢地,令中共解體,好似當年蘇聯既解體令波羅的海三小國可以成功獨立<br />\n<br />\n其實中國真係唔係表面咁團結同堅固,<br />\n區域岐視、南北對立、過去十幾年間偷呃拐騙造成既極端貧富懸殊、新彊西藏內蒙人民既仇恨、貿易戰下預期可見既經濟危機、中共內部黨派鬥爭等等......同埋若果中共成功解體之後,香港人信唔過中國人,可以嘗試用著數招美軍駐港"},{"pid":"178ad2605bcb71c43b421a3a887f7b14beb52c5a","tid":1240091,"uid":49197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T09:25:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://himg2.huanqiu.com/attachment2010/2014/0930/20140930045814218.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhimg2.huanqiu.com%2Fattachment2010%2F2014%2F0930%2F20140930045814218.jpg&h=e825ec9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/11/%E5%88%97%E5%AE%8105.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchinadigitaltimes.net%2Fchinese%2Ffiles%2F2015%2F11%2F%25E5%2588%2597%25E5%25AE%258105.jpg&h=bb9dc71e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i2.read01.com/SIG=3boesi3/3042727432413031.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.read01.com%2FSIG%3D3boesi3%2F3042727432413031.jpg&h=8dd5444b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.read01.com/SIG=2ccdp44/3042727432413036.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.read01.com%2FSIG%3D2ccdp44%2F3042727432413036.jpg&h=80aed944&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i2.read01.com/SIG=20tr